I saw my two boys compete in their first meet this last week. They won, but were sad when I told them that I will not make every competition cause of basketball.
I know we lost, but we gave a great showing for ourselves.
Ran in to some of @HanielLemur wrestling crew. I know some of these guys from the southern Indy circuit.
The phins are not happy. I had to drain the  pool for the winter.  They are being signed for a swim club.
My little girl made a friend with the orca calf next door.  They both enjoy the backyard pool, but that will have to drained for winter soon.
Made it to Arizona.  The house has a pool, which is great for the phins.  My little girl ran around a lot today and wore herself out.  The dry air is different for them.
Well, hitting the road.  A trip cross country was what we wanted for our phins.   Learn that there is more to our nation than just home and grandma and grandpa's.
#TMITuesday  If I dare it today.
Don't leave a phin hangin'  all alone this FA.
Don't forget this phin during FA.
Hitting the gym, but it was good to have Eli and Lucas come over when they could spare the time. They may not have a degree but they can speak the words of a scholar.
Well, ready for anything, I suppose.
We're packing our things just in case.  You don't know what FA holds.
I am rooting for this draft class. My the Good Lord smile upon you all.
I sent my mom two tickets for a week in Cyprus.  She cried, again.  My dad is proud that I can easily afford it.
I have some time today between sets, ask away. #TMITuesday
Everything is calm back home, but the family is quiet like something brewing under the surface. I will answer questions while I wait. #TMITuesday
This FA is truly important.  I have farther than I thought this past season and I am open to an offer, if the contract is truly right.

I knew that coming back home from Hawaii was going to be hard on the little phins, but they are taking it pretty hard.  I was about scold them when Gamama scolded me.  I see family uprooting itself soon.
In a few days we go back to the East Coast.  The little phins love it here.  I can't say that I blame them.
Well, one more week before heading back.  Almost everything is going to be set in place when the day comes.

I am announcing myself for FA.  I am looking to the future and I am planning taking my team to the finals and beyond.  I want to do more than I have already, just give me a chance and let me prove it.
Looking at a local guitar shop here in Hawaii.  The selection is mind-blowing, though one has caught my eye and is definitely coming home with me.
Now that was some spearfishing. @scooniebarrett caught most of the biggest catches yesterday.  Eli won't let Lucas down down for letting that huge one get away.
Congratulations, BIloxi. I am glad the home team won.
#TMITuesday  I am ready for any and all questions.
My sweetie-phin and I went spearfishing.  She is a natural at this, got way more than me.
I guess no one wishes to ask a question.
Not my usual thing, so why not? #TMITuesday
